namic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/124760/', '', 'Gatifloxacin, Rifamycin, Kanamycin, Lomefloxacin, Ampicillin, Ofloxacin, Acyclovir, Netilmicin, Ciprofloxacin, Polymyxin B, Famciclovir, More', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Sipuleucel-T, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Ropeginterferon alfa-2b, Interferon alfacon-1, Sargramostim, Histamine, Pegademase, Pegfilgrastim, More', 1767369485);
